   Amelie Marieって？

   Hello and welcome to my personal blog!

   Living in Tokyo since 2013, I'm a Study Program Coordinator at
   GPlusMedia, the company behind GaijinPot, Japan Today and Savyy Tokyo.

   I love to write about Japanese culture, society and language, and to
   share bits of my life in Japan.

   If you want to read me live, follow me on Twitter.

   Professional Profile
   Go ahead, treat yourself to something else!
